    # "Dad" "I didn't ever really deal with losing her. I just focused on making sure that you were okay."
    "Dad" "Je n'ai jamais vraiment fait le deuil de sa perte. Je me suis juste concentré sur ton bien-être."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:59
translate french u19a1s2_4b604aa5:

    # "Dad" "Then when you left, everything came flooding back again. I couldn't deal with it, [pcname]."
    "Dad" "Puis, quand tu es parti, tout m'est revenu d'un coup. Je n'arrivais pas à le supporter, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:60
translate french u19a1s2_bfcaf31d:

    # "Dad" "I needed her."
    "Dad" "J'avais besoin d'elle."

